n: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000;=
 border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> I like to say</a>, a=
nd sexual harassment is particularly securities fraud. If an executive at a=
 public company sexually harasses colleagues, and the news gets out and the=
