-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> times</a>. Sexual harassment, very=
 much a core form of securities fraud.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Usua=
lly the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission doesn=E2=80=99t bring haras=
sment-as-securities-fraud cases, though; that tends to be reserved for priv=
ate plaintiffs=E2=80=99 lawyers working for shareholders. (I mean, working =
for a chunk of the settlement.) But <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergb=
usiness.com/click/25104125.256842/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9zZ=
