op=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-deco=
ration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00=
0000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">with PSD degrees=
</a>=E2=80=9D: =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/=
click/25104125.256842/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAwOC8wMy8zMC9idXNpb=
mVzcy8zMG1ha2VyLmh0bWw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB6b1081be" itemprop=3D"Story=
Link" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: non=
e !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; borde=
r-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Poor, Smart</a>, with a dee=
p Desire to become rich.=E2=80=9D Wall Street is a place with lots of money=
, and you want junior people who are very motivated by money so they will w=
ork hard; junior people who don=E2=80=99t already have money are more likel=
y to be motivated by it.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand,=
 as I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25104125.256=
842/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDktMjA=
vaW52ZXN0bWVudC1iYW5raW5nLWlzLWNoZWFwLWlmLXlvdS1yZS1yaWNo/607f07ceef4b8524a=
319a23cB372724a0" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"c=
olor: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; =
border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color:=
 #ccc;"> said yesterday</a>, Wall Street is essentially in the business of =
building deep personal relationships with giant piles of money, and if you =
come from money you have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/25104125.256842/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGlj=
bGVzLzIwMTktMDYtMjcvdGlnZXItZ2xvYmFsLXMtY2hhc2UtY29sZW1hbi13YXMtZGVzdGluZWQ=
