=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decora=
tion: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0000=
00; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">better odds of doi=
ng that</a>. If you grow up rich you are more likely to be able to swap sai=
ling anecdotes with a client, or discover that you have neighboring estates=
=C2=A0in Bridgehampton, or =E2=80=94=C2=A0and this is particularly helpful =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0you might be the client=E2=80=99s child. If your mother runs=
 a large public company or a <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness=
.com/click/25104125.256842/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2Fy=
