rtant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-botto=
m-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> state-owned enterprise</a>=C2=A0o=
r a multibillion-dollar family office, and you go to work for an investment=
 bank, that investment bank is more likely to win lucrative business from h=
er, isn=E2=80=99t it? The bank certainly <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/25104125.256842/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9v=
